Package: countiteration
Title: Easy counting of iteration 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mathias", "Delhaye", , "Mathias.Delhaye@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Take in entry a tibble or a dataframe and a variable of interest from that tibble or dataframe. 
             Count the number of iteration for the each possibility of that variable, without taking in account the NA.
             Return a histogram showing in the decreasing order the number of iteration for each possibility. 
